textfsm_template:
Value PORT (\S+)
Value NAME (\S+)
Value STATUS (connected|notconnect)
Value VLAN (\d+)
Value DUPLEX (half|full)
Value SPEED (\S+)
Value TYPE (\S+)

Start
  ^Port\s+Name\s+Status\s+Vlan\s+Duplex\s+Speed\s+Type\s*$$
  ^\s*${PORT}\s+${NAME}\s+${STATUS}\s+${VLAN}\s+${DUPLEX}\s+${SPEED}\s+${TYPE}\s*$$ -> Record
